## Packages 
- **@divineplexus/core**
  - Core nodes, components, and traits. 
- **@divineplexus/editor**
  - The main part of the editor app.
- **@divineplexus/dvefcore**
  - @divinevoxel/foundation core nodes and suppourt.
- **@divineplexus/dvefeditor**
  - @divinevoxel/foundation editor extension.

